actions.name: CancelChangeSet
actions.description: Grants permission to cancel a running change set

actions.name: CompleteTask
actions.description: Grants permission to complete an existing task and submit the content to the associated change

actions.name: DescribeChangeSet
actions.description: Grants permission to return the details of an existing change set

actions.name: DescribeEntity
actions.description: Grants permission to return the details of an existing entity

actions.name: DescribeTask
actions.description: Grants permission to return the details of an existing task

actions.name: ListChangeSets
actions.description: Grants permission to list existing change sets

actions.name: ListEntities
actions.description: Grants permission to list existing entities

actions.name: ListTasks
actions.description: Grants permission to list existing tasks

actions.name: StartChangeSet
actions.description: Grants permission to request a new change set. (Note: resource-level permissions for this action and condition context keys for this action are only supported when used with Catalog API and are not supported when used with AWS Marketplace Management Portal)

actions.name: UpdateTask
actions.description: Grants permission to update the contents of an existing task
